	(7785, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'May you be protected in your crusade. May the Master bless your efforts.', 0),
	(7786, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Even in dreams I did not dare foresee this day.$B$BBehold, mortal.$B$BBEHOLD HE WHO IS OLDER THAN EXISTENCE!$B$BBEHOLD HE WHO HAS FACED TITAN AND GOD ALIKE!$B$BRISE MY MASTER! BREAK FROM YOUR BONDS!', 0),
