	(7843, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I wish I coulda been there to see the look on their faces, mon. Are they packing up their bags? Leavin\' town?$B$BYou done good, $N. Real good. Otho reward you with the big mojo.', 0),
	(7844, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well done, $C. Zul\'jin himself could not have done a better job!', 0),
