	(7848, 1, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'I am now able to transport you to the Molten Core. Ask and it shall be done.', 15354),
	(7849, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'My dearest brother, how I will miss you...$B$BThank you for your assistance, $N. You are truly a hero in my eyes.', 0),
	(7850, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'The dark energy that compels the Vilebranch has been lifted - for now. We must remain ever vigilant in our battle against evil, as even if the Vile Priestess is destroyed, another soon takes her place.', 0),
	(7861, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'A crippling blow to the Vilebranch, indeed. You shall be richly rewarded, $N.', 0),
	(7862, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You are indeed a worthy candidate for the new position, $N. Accept this trinket as a token of our appreciation for your hard work. I will be reviewing all applications next year.', 0),
	(7863, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Warsong Gulch. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Gulch, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Friendly with us, and bandages when you are Honored.', 0),
	(7864, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You\'ve certainly begun to prove yourself to us, $N. As a reward, please take this care package! Inside it you\'ll find rations and bandages that are usable only inside Warsong Gulch. $B$BAs you continue to prove yourself inside the Gulch, you\'ll find that these items will become available to you for purchase. Rations become available when you are Friendly with us, and bandages when you are Honored.', 0),
