	(7874, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Captain Shatterskull roars in triumph.>$B$BHow much more can they withstand? How many more Alliance filth must perish at the hands of the Horde for them to retreat? Only time will tell, $R.', 0),
	(7875, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, '<Captain Shatterskull roars in triumph.>$B$BHow much more can they withstand? How many more Alliance filth must perish at the hands of the Horde for them to retreat? Only time will tell, $R.', 0),
