	(8181, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'So, you have been speaking with that old dwarf Ironboot and uncovered the lost Mosh\'aru Tablets, have you?  That meddling prospector...$B$BNo matter.  It is too late to save this world.  Hakkar has been reborn, and even now grows in power... deep in the ancient troll kingdom of Zul\'Gurub!  He has come!  And he will rule in blood and terror!$B$BThank you, $N.  Your help has sped the return of the Soulflayer!', 0),
