	(8194, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'This deal works for me if it works for you!', 0),
	(8195, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Excellent - this set of coins will make a fine addition to our growing collection... one that we will use in the tribe\'s defense against the rise of the Blood God. You\'ve earned this Honor Token, $N, as well as the thanks of the tribe!', 0),
