	(8227, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Why, you found my favorite measuring tape! I love this tape! I measured some of the biggest fish I ever caught with it...$B$BBut, I lost this tape in Zul\'Gurub... you\'ve been to Zul\'Gurub? Did you see the fabled Gahz\'ranka?$B$BWell... do you want to catch him?', 0),
