	(8232, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You have learned the old ways, $N, and for that I offer you a gift from my days as a $C.', 0),
	(8233, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Welcome, welcome, welcome!  Please, $N, have a seat and discuss a simple matter with me.$B$BYou see, $N, I\'ve recently lost something dear to me, and to put it bluntly, I want it back at all costs.  There\'s something in it for you, don\'t worry about that!  Oh yes, something very nice.$B$BNow, what say you $N... are you up for some adventure?', 0),
