	(8240, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Excellent... each bijou we wrest away from the Blood God\'s minions is one step closer we all are to finally defeating them once and for all.  You bring honor to the Zandalar - and yourself - through your noble actions.$B$BRemember $N, you may always destroy the bijous you find in Zul\'Gurub at the altar.  For each one, you will gain recognition and an Honor Token!  Just remember to have an open space in your inventory if you don\'t have one of the tokens already.', 0),
	(8241, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'There\'s always room for more fiery flux, junior. Keep it comin\'... unless I tell you to stop.', 0),
