	(8730, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Vaelastrasz\'s soul is at ease, champion. The Aspects all watch your progress with great interest. Know that you have powerful allies.$B$BI was commanded to grant you something to aid you in this struggle. Use it well...', 0),
