	(9067, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You\'re quite the energetic young $gman:woman;, aren\'t you?$B$BThis all looks very adequate. You certainly deserve compensation for gathering up all of this for me, and something a little extra I think.$B$BOh, I almost forgot, here\'s an invitation to the party. And, $c, next time that you drop in make sure to dress up in something a little more... festive.', 0),
