	(13830, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'So eating it makes you invisible... what a strange defense this clever fish has developed.$b$bI\'d like to digest this for a bit.  Pun not intended, $N.  Really.  Why don\'t you come see me tomorrow?', 15354),
	(13832, 1, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Well now, that looks like it could be valuable.  Difficult to know until it\'s cleaned up and appraised, but I\'m still willing to make the trade if you are.', 15354),
