	(24667, 5, 1, 274, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'Is this from Crawgol? Wonderful! Despite all the turmoil in the world, we can\'t turn our back on the silithid threat. It is important to have people like Crawgol studying our enemy closely and learning its secrets for the fight ahead!$B$B<Tauna opens the book and glances over the first page. Her face falls.>$B$BOh. Well. I suppose it\'s something, at least. ', 15354),
