	(24848, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 'You... You\'re not Snivel. Did he send you? He\'s so late, I had started to give up hope...$B$B<Tears start welling up in the woman\'s eyes once she realizes that you aren\'t there to deliver a message from Snivel.>$B$BThat\'s not like my Snivel, but what choice is there?', 0),
